social_posts.post_text: Simplify food at your holiday party with an easy #ToastBar which is sure to be a crowd pleaser! Get my recipes and tips at the link in my bio @pagingsupermom 👈 https://pagingsupermom.com/how-have-toast-bar/

So much fun to watch #Christmastime coming to life around here! We rotate which kid gets to put the star on the tree and it’s @piperpointe year! Also love being under the mistletoe with @toddbridges 😘 #christmasdecor #mistletoe #deckthehalls #merrychristmas

So excited that there is a #LightTheWorld #GivingMachine close by this year! I’ve been to them in Hawaii and Utah, but it’s fun to be able to bring the kids this year!!! 🎄 It’s essentially a charity vending machine and visiting the machines with all the Christmas lights was such a fun family outing. In AZ there are #GivingMachines in Downtown Glendale’s town square where #GlendaleGiltters is held and also in Old Town Gilbert by the water tower. #familytraditions #christmastime #sharegoodness Find a Giving Machine near you using the link in my bio @pagingsupermom

Trying to get things on track in the new year? I just reread this article I wrote several years ago to help mama’s get life organized! I shared a bundle of free organization printables too 🙌 #linkinbio https://pagingsupermom.com/organize-declutter-getting-things-done/

Pretty cool having the #SuperBowl in town! We went to the @nike outlet near the stadium so my nine-year-old could cash in the money he’s been saving for a pair of #AirJordans. It was fun to see the setup, but we’ll definitely be steering clear of the stadium this weekend! #superbowl57 #superbowl2023 #superbowllvii

Went to @bouncethemallusa today with my sister and adorable niece! Her favorite was definitely the colorful disco bouncy house where everyone had music-playing headphones. It was getting pretty hot☀️ in Phoenix this weekend, but I’d bet it would be nice in Indianapolis where #BounceTheMall is headed next. Super-Tip: 15% discount code: SUPER15 💖 We think this bouncy fun park is ideal for kids 8+ #bouncypark #bouncethemallusa

I’m a big fan of Arizona sunsets #☀️ #arizona #phoenix #sunset #sunsets #azsunset

So proud of this girl @attalieanne! As parents we don’t often get much sense of completion… the house never stays clean; people keep getting hungry again no matter how good dinner was last night; laundry is a never-ending, vicious cycle… so it was such a pleasure to mark the accomplishments of my first born with her high school graduation 🥳 I am so excited to see where life takes her. I mean right now she’s in THAILAND so there’s no telling what’s next. I love you Attalie! 💕 #highschoolgraduate #proudmomma #supermommoment

Cashed in my #MothersDay gift for a fantastic dinner downtown with this cute guy @toddbridges! I’ve wanted to go to The Compass revolving restaurant at @hyattphoenix since I was in high school, and it did not disappoint. The octopus was delicious #dinnerdate #toddbridges #hyattphoenix #compassrestaurant #datenight

So grateful for my wonderful Father! I don’t think he even has Instagram but wanted to be sure he was nominated for #WorldsGreatestDad because he sure deserves it! He’s such a hard worker, incredibly smart, and I’ve learned so much from him #thanksDad #happyfathersday

May be one of the best uses for a pool noodle I’ve ever come up with. ⛵️ These pool noodle sailboats we made years ago have stood the test of time because they are a lot of fun for ALL ages.
